<div class="thumbinner" style="width:352px;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Cjsflowco.svg" class="image"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/eb/Cjsflowco.svg/350px-Cjsflowco.svg.png" width="350" height="213" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/eb/Cjsflowco.svg/525px-Cjsflowco.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/eb/Cjsflowco.svg/700px-Cjsflowco.svg.png 2x" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Cjsflowco.svg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="http://bits.wikimedia.org/static-1.21wmf9/skins/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
United States criminal justice system flowchart.</div>
</div>
